{"type":"question","id":21623,"title":"冷戰時期Bratislava的邊境是怎麼樣的？","uid":23944,"topics":[7643,2036,7644,7645],"contents":"Bratislava當年是捷克斯洛伐克大城市之一，現在是斯洛伐克首都，就在奧地利邊界旁邊，那麼冷戰期間當地邊境是什麼樣的呢？怎麼防止人跑到奧地利去？<br>\n<br>\n我查了一下英文資料也找不到。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/59/Bratislava_Montage.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/59/Bratislava_Montage.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/59/Bratislava_Montage.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-03-21","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}